dc_title_s: Proposed Development, Conceptual Site Plans: Prince George's County, Maryland
dc_description_s: This data set is a depiction of the bacis relationships among the propesed uses and illustrates the approximate loactions of structures, parking areas, streets, site access, open space and other major physical features. They may be somewhat detailed, or may depict large areas connected with arrows or other graphic symbols. Conceptual site plans must be approved before a preliminary plan of subdivision may be approved. They are valid indefinitely.
